snippet.title: JDM: Japanese Drift Master | Release Date Announcement
snippet.description:
✅ Wishlist JDM now at https://cutt.ly/JDM-Steam

The streets of Guntama will be yours to conquer starting May 21st, 2025! Start your engines and prepare for the ultimate drifting adventure. Watch the trailer for an exclusive sneak peek of the action-packed gameplay!

🎵 Goodbye Setsuna - Hikigane
